om\": 575, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\"}, {\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Schelstraete\", \"score\": 0.9999880939516794, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Victor Schelstraete\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Schelstraete\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Schelstraete\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9845988847526971, \"rank\": 0.015609877178578532, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 25-year-old did receive some help from Papua New Guinea's boxing coach Peter Morrison, he was beaten handily by Schelstraete, who left the Samoan bleeding from the cheek.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\", \"score\": 0.582283679898821, \"rank\": 0.5889216176202127, \"text\": \"Papua New Guinea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Papua_New_Guinea\"}, {\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\", \"score\": 0.9999999865933661, \"rank\": 7.094173477633044e-09, \"text\": \"Peter Morrison\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Morrison\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"score\": 0.9974935142318698, \"rank\": 0.001760911363077064, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was thinking about pulling out \\u2026 it's been hard,\\\" Pacific Games champion Plodzicki-Faoagali said.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been hard to stay strong.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been struggling mentally the past few days.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought I was going to win a medal for sure, but it's been really hard mentally.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care about the medal right now.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even through these hard times, I appreciate everyone.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to come back stronger and chase my dreams.\\\"\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Schelstraete, who spoke to Plodzicki-Faoagali before and after the fight and held up his opponent's arm in the ring, said the Samoan had displayed great spirit just by showing up.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"score\": 0.9974935142318698, \"rank\": 0.001760911363077064, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Big respect to him.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got a big heart.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He honored his coach by fighting,\\\" Schelstraete said.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These coaches, they are very selfless.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They put in all their work for us to get here, and for him to not be here to experience that moment, it's very sad.\\\"\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if it was hard to fight in the bout, Schelstraete said: \\\"I had to put that aside.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I felt genuinely sorry for him.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you have to put the emotions aside.\\\"\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Schelstraete meets Spain's Enmanuel Reyes on Thursday.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5948378229097768, \"rank\": 0.6053585710415421, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}]}"